#: ../../developer/services/admin-api.rst:10 12ef5ccc8f5a4e98a66ef85fcb6f4367
msgid ""
"The goals of the Admin API system is to provide a way for the user to "
"manage the domains without direct access to dom0."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/services/admin-api.rst:13 8059dcb8d04b46359edd663e9d0c7e1f
msgid "Foreseen benefits include:"
