msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/services/admin-api.rst:16 49144c1c071b40f6864bd65eec710923
msgid ""
"Possibility to create multi-user system, where different users are able "
"to use different sets of domains, possibly overlapping. This would also "
"require to have separate GUI domain."
msgstr ""

